# @no-proxy

### Group Endpoints
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@userId = ad7a53cb-ee8c-4172-9118-0d0ec148c366
@groupId = 5bb8c872-f87c-4486-a239-ca0d70698a2f


### List All Groups
GET {{baseUrl}}/groups


### Get Specific Group
GET {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}


### Create Group
POST {{baseUrl}}/groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "NGR 10",
  "group_leader_id": null
}

