### Join Group
POST {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}/join?user_id={{userId}}


### List Group Members
GET {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}/members


### Set Group Leader
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}/leader
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}"
}
